::Striker/Mosquitor::

Striker looks at Rhinox. "Welcome in." He says, "Computer, let unit Rhinox 
through." He says slightly louder and the Ark lowers the shields.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Mosquitor flies out of the base as Scorpinok's missile hits it.

"Invader!!" He yells, ignoring Scorpinok's speach and firing firing acid at 
him.
